title: Tasty Cajun Rice & Turkey Burrito | Jamie Oliver & Uncle Ben's
description:
(PP) Contains product placement. Check out this amazing new burrito recipe from Jamie Oliver. It was recorded as part of Food Tube's live cookalong with Uncle Ben's. It's a great way to use up leftover Turkey and perfect for chicken too. A great Thanksgiving and Christmas recipe so keep it handy!

This recipe uses Uncle Ben's wholegrain rice pouch | https://unclebens.co.uk

For other great ways to cook rice from scratch check out http://youtu.be/gx9h65E433M

Jamie is joined by Food Tube's Queen of home cooking, Kerryann Dunlop. Watch her simple Chicken Curry recipe here http://youtu.be/Pc4OMXbpyus

Head over to Drinks Tube for a great cocktail that goes with this dish http://jamieol.com/blbAFD
And be sure to take a look at our food and drink pairing website  http://jamieol.com/OLf5Kt
